reviewText: This is a 'slow-burn' movie ... give it a chance and it will suck you in.  This is one of the best movies you've never heard of.

Biased opinion since my step-son plays Antinio ;)
A fun watch. IIRC the French review was along the lines of "Tarantino without the gore"
GREAT movie to watch after a bad day at work!!
Pretty funny random Coolio indie movie...soundtrack really cool. Movie is dark humor but funny
